# Dataset

The raw image dataset is not uploaded to this repository due to privacy and file size concerns.

The dataset was collected locally using a webcam connected to Raspberry Pi.

## Dataset Summary

| Class | Number of Images |
|---|---:|
| helmet | 150 |
| no_helmet | 150 |
| Total | 300 |

## Local Directory Structure

```text
data/raw/
├── helmet/
│   └── 150 images
└── no_helmet/
    └── 150 images
